url=https://pao-pao.net/about-us | title=关于泡泡 | publisher=泡泡網民報告 | accessdate=2015-04-12 | language=zh-hans | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315025744/https://pao-pao.net/about-us | archivedate=2015-03-15 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.solidot.org/story?sid=38506 | title=GreatFire.org合作新闻网站被屏蔽 | publisher=[[Solidot|Solidot]] | date=2015-02-27 | accessdate=2015-04-12 | language=zh-cn | archive-date=2020-02-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200214225057/https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=38506 | dead-url=yes}}</ref>、[[英國廣播公司|英國廣播公司]]（BBC）。

== 项目 ==

=== 免翻墙镜像 ===
2013年11月，[[路透社|路透社]]网站被中国政府屏蔽，GreatFire随即在[[Amazon_S3|Amazon S3]]上建立了其镜像站点<ref name=seethrough>{{cite web|url=https://zh.greatfire.org/blog/2013/nov/look-ma-i-can-see-through-great-firewall|date=2013-11-17|author=charlie|website=zh.greatfire.org|title=哈，中国防火长城漏风了！|access-date=2021-10-13|archive-date=2022-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220114221227/https://zh.greatfire.org/blog/2013/nov/look-ma-i-can-see-through-great-firewall}}</ref>，声称无法被屏蔽，并建议[[习近平|习近平]]解除所有封锁，“闪电般进行解封”，“作为真正的改革者而功垂千古”。<ref name=seethrough/>

2014年11月，GreatFire與BBC合作，讓中國大陸網路用戶能夠連線到被防火長城封鎖的[[BBC中文網|BBC中文網]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://zh.greatfire.org/blog/2014/nov/greatfireorg-unblocks-bbc-chinese|date=2014-11-24|title=GreatFire解封BBC中文网|author=charlie|website=zh.greatfire.org|access-date=2021-10-13|archive-date=2021-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211102152236/https://zh.greatfire.org/blog/2014/nov/greatfireorg-unblocks-bbc-chinese}}</ref><ref name="GigaOM-BBC-Collateral-Freedom-Bypass-Chinese-Censorship">{{cite web | url=https://gigaom.com/2014/11/24/bbc-uses-collateral-freedom-system-to-bypass-chinese-censorship/ | title=BBC uses “collateral freedom” system to bypass Chinese censorship | publisher=Gigaom, Inc. | work=GigaOM | date=2014-11-24 | accessdate=2015-04-11 | author=Meyer, David | archive-date=2020-11-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130174008/https://gigaom.com/2014/11/24/bbc-uses-collateral-freedom-system-to-bypass-chinese-censorship/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="GreatFire-BBC-Punch-Uncensored-News-Through-GFW">{{cite web | url=http://betanews.com/2014/11/25/greatfire-org-and-bbc-punch-uncensored-news-through-the-great-firewall-of-china/ | title=GreatFire.org and BBC punch uncensored news through the Great Firewall of China | publisher=BetaNews, Inc. | work=BetaNews | date=2014-11-25 | accessdate=2015-04-11 | author=Wilson, Mark | archive-date=2015-04-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414071232/http://betanews.com/2014/11/25/greatfire-org-and-bbc-punch-uncensored-news-through-the-great-firewall-of-china/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Slate-BBC-Working-With-Transparency-Group-Uncensored-News-China">{{cite web | url=http://www.slate.com/blogs/future_tense/2014/11/25/greatfire_org_and_the_bbc_are_using_the_collateral_freedom_approach_to_offer.html | title=The BBC Is Working With a Transparency Group to Bring Uncensored News Into China | publisher=The Slate Group LLC | work=Slate | date=2014-11-25 | accessdate=2015-04-11 | author=Newman, Lily Hay | language=en | archive-date=2018-09-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180916002219/http://www.slate.com/blogs/future_tense/2014/11/25/greatfire_org_and_the_bbc_are_using_the_collateral_freedom_approach_to_offer.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

透過[[依附的自由|依附的自由]]技術，GreatFire網站也架設其他相似的[[鏡像站|鏡像站]]，有[[Google|Google]]、[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]及[[德國之聲|德國之聲]]等被封鎖的網站，以及在[[GitHub|GitHub]]上建立連結目錄，普遍使用的[[內容傳遞網路|內容傳遞網路]]像是[[Amazon_CloudFront|Amazon CloudFront]]和[[CloudFlare|CloudFlare]]，讓網路封鎖系統因要花太多資源而放棄封鎖。<ref name="OpenITP-Collateral-Freedom">{{cite web |url=https://www.upturn.org/static/files/CollateralFreedom.pdf |title=Collateral Freedom - A Snapshot of Chinese Internet Users Circumventing Censorship |publisher=Open Internet Tools Project |date= |accessdate=2021-10-09 |author1=Robinson, David |author2=Yu, Harlan |author3=An, Anne |deadurl=no |archive-date=2022-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120150100/https://www.upturn.org/static/files/CollateralFreedom.pdf }}</ref><ref name=notsogreat>{{cite web|url=https://zh.greatfire.org/blog/2015/mar/collateral-freedom-and-not-so-great-firewall|title="依附的自由"和不那么伟大的防火墙|date=2015-03-11|author=charlie|website=zh.greatfire.org|access-date=2021-10-09|archive-date=2021-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211102152218/https://zh.greatfire.org/blog/2015/mar/collateral-freedom-and-not-so-great-firewall}}</ref><ref name="GreatFire-Collateral-Freedom-FAQ">{{cite web | url=https://zh.greatfire.org/blog/2014/jan/collateral-freedom-faq | title=Collateral Freedom FAQ | publisher=GreatFire.org | date=2014-01-07 | accessdate=2015-04-11 | language=en | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150424131222/https://zh.greatfire.org/blog/2014/jan/collateral-freedom-faq | archivedate=2015-04-24 }}</ref>

2015年3月，GreatFire的镜像站受到大量[[分散式阻斷服務攻擊|分散式阻斷服務攻擊 (DDoS)]]，<ref name=paopao>{{cite web | url=https://pao-pao.net/article/396 | title=互联网自由在中国遭受新攻击 | publisher=泡泡網民報告 | date=2015-03-20 | accessdate=2015-04-12 | language=zh-hans | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150927113644/https://pao-pao.net/article/396 | archivedate=2015-09-27 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://zh.greatfire.org/blog/2015/mar/we-are-under-attack|date=2015-03-19|title=我们正被攻击|author=charlie|quote=攻击开始于3月17日，我们每小时都要收到高达26亿的请求，这是大约正常水平的2500倍以上。|access-date=2021-10-09|deadurl=no|website=zh.greatfire.org|archive-date=2021-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211125094135/https://zh.greatfire.org/blog/2015/mar/we-are-under-attack}}</ref>疑似被中國政府的網路攻擊工具[[大炮_(中國網路審查)|大炮]]鎖定，被導入大量的[[網路流量|網路流量]]。
随后，其托管在GitHub的两个项目主页也成为攻击目标。<ref name="Activists-Plotting-to-End-Censorship-in-China">{{cite web | url=http://techcrunch.com/2015/03/30/greatfire/ | title=These Activists Are Plotting To End Internet Censorship In China | publisher=AOL Inc. | work=TechCrunch | date=2015-03-30 | accessdate=2015-04-10 | author=Russel, Jon | archive-date=2020-11-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126120322/https://techcrunch.com/2015/03/30/greatfire/ | dead-url=no }}</ref> <ref name="NYT-China-Said-to-Use-Powerful-New-Weapon-Censor-Internet">{{cite web | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/11/technology/china-is-said-to-use-powerful-new-weapon-to-censor-internet.html | title=China Is Said to Use Powerful New Weapon to Censor Internet | publisher=The New York Times Company | work=The New York Times | date=2015-04-10 | accessdate=2015-04-11 | author=Perlroth, Nicole | language=en | archive-date=2015-04-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150411005836/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/11/technology/china-is-said-to-use-powerful-new-weapon-to-censor-internet.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>
{{see also|对GitHub的审查和封锁#DDoS攻击}}

这些镜像站后来继续运作了一段时间<ref name=paopao/>，直到2016年7月26日Greatfire从其GitHub主页移除镜像站相关内容。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://github.com/greatfire/wiki/commit/88fcd2c96a4d3723be73ee0d15c4fcf0241ba7ca|date=2016-07-26|access-date=2021-10-09|title=commit 88fcd2c96a4|website=GitHub|archive-date=2021-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211009130437/https://github.com/greatfire/wiki/commit/88fcd2c96a4d3723be73ee0d15c4fcf0241ba7ca}}</ref>

=== 测试器 ===

{{PAGENAME}}網站也提供測試系統，称为 {{lang|en|GreatFire Analyzer}}，讓用戶能夠即時測試特定網站或关键字是否遭到防火長城封鎖。該页面声称「带给您中国防火墙封锁的最新资讯」<ref name="GreatFire-Online-Censorship-China">{{cite web | url=https://zh.greatfire.org/analyzer | title=中国的网络审查 GreatFire.org | publisher=GreatFire.org | accessdate=2015-04-11 | dead-url=no | archive-date=2022-04-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220412152456/https://zh.greatfire.org/analyzer }}</ref>。
GreatFire还提供了另一个测试系统：[https://blocky.greatfire.org/ Blocky] {{Wayback|url=https://blocky.greatfire.org/ |date=20210527014143 }}，该网站能够测试某一个域名及其关联域名遭到GFW封锁的情况，并能够提供详细的测试数据报告。

